			<div>The health and safety of our students is our priority.  We appreciate the patience and understanding of the Bonsall school community as we work through the preparedness and prevention of COVID-19.  District leadership and the appropriate staff have been participating in ongoing planning and communication led by the San Diego County Office of Education to receive the most recent and relevant guidance for schools.  We are being guided in our response by the County of San Diego Health and Human Services Department.</div>
<div> </div>
<div>A chronology of district-to-home communication will be posted below for reference, along with links to relevant resources to ensure everyone remains up-to-date with accurate details and guidance.</div>
